OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FSouthampton community leaders have
OL,7,Faccused the far right of bussing
OL,8,Fpeople into the city to "fuel"
OL,9,Fviolence to further their own agenda
OL,10,Ffollowing the murder of Henry Nowak.
OL,12,FJohn Savage, a Labour representative
OL,13,Ffor the Portswood ward of Southampton
OL,14,FCity Council where the disorder took
OL,15,Fplace, described the violence as
OL,16,F"absolutely outrageous".
OL,18,FHe said that it occurred against a
OL,19,Fbackdrop of long-standing protests
OL,20,Fagainst a hotel in the area used to
OL,21,Fhouse asylum-seekers.
OL,26,@pD@YOUpD@^O]xD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FMr Savage said: "We really need to
OL,7,Fwait for the outcome of the IOPC
OL,8,F(Independent Office for Police
OL,9,FConduct) investigation, we can't make
OL,10,Fany judgement based on seeing a couple
OL,11,Fof seconds of a video, however
OL,12,Fdistressing it is.
OL,14,F"Most people are really upset by it,
OL,15,Fthey really care about what happened
OL,16,Fin the last minutes of a poor 18-year-
OL,17,Fold student's life, but it doesn't
OL,18,Fwarrant the violent, disrupting,
OL,19,Fdamaging behaviour we saw last night,
OL,20,Fwe need to wait to find out what
OL,21,Fhappened."
OL,26,@nD@QOUvD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
