CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FMr Savage described Portswood as a
OL,7,F"progressive" area with many students
OL,8,Fand university staff living there and
OL,9,Fsaid he believed most of the
OL,10,Fdemonstrators were from other parts of
OL,11,Fthe city as well as elsewhere in the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FHe said: "It's absolutely outrageous,
OL,15,Fthese are people who have been bussed
OL,16,Fin from other places to cause mayhem
OL,17,Fin our city."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]vD@JOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FHe added: "Mark Nowak, Henry's father,
OL,7,Fclearly stated that he didn't want
OL,8,Fanything to cause further division and
OL,9,Ftension in the area and that's exactly
OL,10,Fwhat has happened it seems they are
OL,11,Fdoing it for their own aims, their own
OL,12,Fagenda and it's not welcome here."
OL,14,FSarah Bogle, the Labour leader of the
OL,15,Fcity council, said that she believed a
OL,16,Fnumber of people had arrived in the
OL,17,Fcity from elsewhere for the
OL,18,Fdemonstration. It started outside the
OL,19,Fcity's central police station and
OL,20,Fwhich was attended by political
OL,21,Factivist Tommy Robinson.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FShe said: "They were pretty awful
OL,7,Fscenes last night and very unwelcome
OL,8,Fto see that level of disturbance in
OL,9,Fwhat is normally a very quiet
OL,10,Fneighbourhood."
OL,12,FCalling for calm to allow the IOPC
OL,13,Fprobe to conclude, she said: "It's
OL,14,Fvery very distressing to see what's
OL,15,Fhappened and it's such an awful
OL,16,Ftragedy and I really want to respect
OL,17,Fand support the principles of Henry
OL,18,FNowak's family's wishes to dial down
OL,19,Fthe rhetoric, dial down the tensions,
OL,20,Fand keep the peace and keep people
OL,21,Fsafe and to honour his memory.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@OO]uD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,F"It's a huge tragedy for him and his
OL,7,Ffamily and it's awful when these
OL,8,Ftragedies are weaponised by people who
OL,9,Fshould know better, whether it's
OL,10,Fpoliticians or the far right ` it
OL,11,Freally is unwelcome."
OL,13,FShe added: "People have the right to
OL,14,Fprotest, which is fine, but to
OL,15,Factually then go and just basically
OL,16,Fcause distress, I mean people couldn't
OL,17,Feven get home that evening, that's
OL,18,Freally not acceptable."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]uD@LOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
