CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FChief Constable Alexis Boon, of
OL,7,FHampshire Constabulary, said that
OL,8,Fthose involved in the disorder had
OL,9,Fbeen "determined to spark fear and
OL,10,Fdivision".
OL,12,FShe said: "What we, as a society,
OL,13,Fcannot accept is the violent scenes we
OL,14,Fsaw in Southampton last night.
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@IO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,F"Some clearly arrived intent on
OL,7,Fcausing disorder and trouble. We saw
OL,8,Fbottles thrown, makeshift weapons
OL,9,Fused, damage caused to the homes and
OL,10,Fvehicles of innocent residents and
OL,11,Fthreats and violence directed towards
OL,12,Four officers.
OL,14,F"As a result, 11 officers and one
OL,15,Fpolice dog were injured, while trying
OL,16,Fto do their job to protect the
OL,17,Fcommunities that we serve."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FShe added: "My officers bravely and
OL,7,Frobustly faced violence with
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and courage last night
OL,9,Fand this morning our investigation is
OL,10,Funder way to identify those
OL,11,Fresponsible for the disorder.
OL,13,F"Last night, we made two arrests and
OL,14,Fthat number will rise as those
OL,15,Finvestigations continue."
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
