OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FMs Boon added: "I know that since the
OL,7,Frelease of the body-worn video footage
OL,8,Ffrom the night of Henry Nowak's
OL,9,Fmurder, there is a desire for answers
OL,10,Fand accountability but that must be
OL,11,Fdone in the right way and not used as
OL,12,Fan excuse to threaten and intimidate
OL,13,Fmy officers and bring violence to our
OL,14,Fstreets causing fear and harm to those
OL,15,Fliving and working in Hampshire and
OL,16,Fthe Isle of Wight."
OL,26,@nD@POUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
