FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,FCaroline Nokes, Conservative MP for
OL,7,FRomsey and Southampton North, said:
OL,8,F"The Sikh community forms a
OL,9,Fsignificant part of Southampton's
OL,10,Fsocial fabric, particularly within the
OL,11,FSouthampton North part of my
OL,12,Fconstituency.
OL,14,F"Swaythling is home to one of the
OL,15,Fcity's gurdwaras, and I know how
OL,16,Fanxious members of the Sikh faith in
OL,17,Fthe city feel right now.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,F"The city needs calm, restraint and
OL,7,Frespect for the rule of law. We owe
OL,8,Fthat to Henry's family and friends,
OL,9,Fwho continue to live with the
OL,10,Fconsequences of this tragedy every
OL,11,Fday."
OL,13,FWhilst, Darren Paffey, MP for
OL,14,FSouthampton Itchen, and Satvir Kaur,
OL,15,FMP for Southampton Test, issued a
OL,16,Fjoint statement saying: "The appalling
OL,17,Fscenes we saw yesterday evening have
OL,18,Fno place in our city.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,F"The senseless murder of Henry Nowak
OL,7,Fand the police response have provoked
OL,8,Fstrong feelings and raised serious
OL,9,Fquestions that need answering. These
OL,10,Fare understandable and legitimate, and
OL,11,Fwe have both been clear about the need
OL,12,Ffor transparency and accountability.
OL,14,F"But we should also be clear about the
OL,15,Fviolence that we saw last night. This
OL,16,Fwas not a lawful and peaceful protest.
OL,17,FInstead, it was the grotesque and
OL,18,Fcynical spectacle of a young man's
OL,19,Fdeath being used to whip up division,
OL,20,Finflame tensions, and provoke criminal
OL,21,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780575067
OL,3,CSouthampton community leaders accuse
OL,4,Cfar right of fuelling violence
OL,6,F"Henry's family have said that they do
OL,7,Fnot want his death to be used to
OL,8,Fcreate tension. Most of us in
OL,9,FSouthampton will rightly choose to
OL,10,Frespect the wishes of a grieving
OL,11,Ffamily while allowing the proper
OL,12,Fprocesses to run their course. Those
OL,13,Fwho don't are wrong. The violence and
OL,14,Fdisorder we saw yesterday can never be
OL,15,Fjustified and should not be repeated.
OL,17,F"And to those who choose to come to
OL,18,Four city and hijack this tragedy to
OL,19,Fstoke hatred: you are not wanted here."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
